  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Protest tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power Minister Kanjana Wijesekara said that the trade unions of the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation (CIPETCO), which are associated with political parties, will carry out a protest tomorrow (22).",
        "The minister noted that the unions of the petroleum corporation have opposed the proposed restructuring plans to be carried out in the corporation.",
        "The minister indicated that although the right to protest was not challenged, both the petroleum and power sectors should be restructured and necessary steps would be taken.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Minister recently appointed a seven-member committee to reorganize the Petroleum Corporation and the Sri Lanka Electricity Board.",
        "The committee is tasked with evaluating companies suitable for importing, distributing and selling petroleum products.",
        "It is worth noting that in Sri Lanka many companies will be involved in the petroleum industry along with Sibetco and IOC."
      ],
